FBIS3-41069 "jptdd005__l94006" JPRS-TDD-94-005-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 1 February 1994 LATIN AMERICA BOLIVIA Deputies `Confirm' Existence of DEA Communications `Center' PY2501180794 La Paz Television Nacional Network in Spanish 1700 GMT 25 Jan 94 PY2501180794 La Paz Television Nacional Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] A delegation of deputies headed by [Democratic Socialism Alternative Deputy] Jerjes Justiniano, [Patriotic Accord Deputy] Guido Nayar, and prosecutor Freddy Flores, has confirmed the existence of a DEA center for intercepting telephone and radio communications of [Santa Cruz] Department officials. The delegation visited a property, allegedly owned by the DEA, where the existence of the center had been reported, at kilometer 11 of the highway to Cotoca.
